  <WULA_Colony_Promotion.LetterTextGuestLost.slateRef>需要你护卫的{SUBJECT_definite}失踪在你的殖民地。[failLetterEndingCommon]</WULA_Colony_Promotion.LetterTextGuestLost.slateRef>
